item.title: About
item.author: alaiksander@gmail.com (alaiksander)
item.description: I’m a father of three beautiful kids and a husband of one loving wife. Born and raised by teachers made me one of them. A fortunate event that my wife is and her parents were also teachers. Presently living in Demak with my family. I teach Islamic Junior High School Students and love doing a little coding with my 10 years old x200 thinkpad.
